data.description: French country home with amazing views of the lake, mountains & sunsets. Close to downtown Ashland. Reclaimed wood beams, solid wood doors, trim and baseboards throughout. 20+ acres including its own small vineyard providing outstanding Tempranillo wine. Large island in the gourmet kitchen with Viking appliances. Including double convection oven, 6 burner gas cooktop, built in wine refrigerator, granite countertops, hardwood floors, and large butler pantry.  6 fireplaces and a 5-car garage. Beautiful library/office with fireplace, large windows and ceilings to take in the forever views. Large covered/uncovered patio areas with fireplace and built in BBQ, and living area. Tranquil courtyard with separate studio that has vaulted ceilings, formal living & dinning room, plus bonus room. This house has it all, approximately 6331 SQFT. This is country living at its finest and just outside of Ashland.
